
Step 1 
Project has "not" been done using Maven due to issues in network and downloading jars 
Uploaded all required libraries in 3 zip folders lib1,lib2 and lib3 Unzip from these.

Step 2 
Unzip main project web-customer-tracker 
and combine all libraries extracted in step 1 into web-customer-tracker\WebContent\WEB-INF\lib folders

Step 3 
create schema in mysql with user springstudent and password springstudent.
then run the attached SQL.txt 

Step 4 
Import the project in eclipse make sure to have all the libaries in reference libraries

Have attached screenshot for references of working code. 